Two independent client-side bugs: (1) both `useAddAdapter` and `AdapterSetupWizard` fire success toasts on adapter add, and (2) `extractAdapterId` regex matches `relay.adapter.<id>.*` but current subjects use `relay.human.<platform>.<chatId>`.

